This is a very simple Android app that displays the GPS coordinates.
It does only the following
- Displays longitude and latitude
- Displays speed, altitude and accuracy and number of satellites.

This app doesn't require any internet connection.
This app only uses the GPS as for the location.

This app does NOT:
- Display a map with a route.
- Record a GPX trace

Privacy:

This app doesn't collect or store any information on the device or send any information to third
party servers
